1. *Želiš* li otići u šetnju? (Do you want to go for a walk?) 
2. On *želi* da ode u Holandiju. (He wants to go to Holland.)
3. Ona *želiše* da putuje u Evropu. (She wanted to travel to Europe.)
4. Mi *želimo* da vidimo Pariz. (We want to see Paris.)
5. Oni *žele* da kupe novo auto. (They want to buy a new car.)